h3 States

| Text inputs has three states vailable:

ul
  li success: <code>c-input--success</code>
  li warning: <code>c-input--warning</code>
  li danger: <code>c-input--danger</code>

.c-mb4.c-mt2
  div(style="max-width:30rem")
    input(type="text", class="c-input c-input--success", placeholder="Placeholder", value="Sample Text")

  :code(lang="html")
    <input type="text" class="c-input c-input--success" placeholder="Placeholder" value="Sample Text">

.c-mb4.c-mt2
